Description_lang: The magic of the dance enthralls players, applying $s2 stacks of $@spellname347350 for $d. Each time the player jumps, $347434s1 Shadow damage is inflicted to all players and a stack of $@spellname347350 is removed.Players who fail to remove all stacks before $d are slain.
AuraDescription_lang: Jumping inflicts $347434s1 Shadow damage to all players and removes an stack of $@spellname347350.Upon expiration the wearer is slain.
